lmc / listmodifierchar        Lists speedwalk modifier characters
 
   Format:
      ;lmc                    Lists modifier characters
      
   Notes:
      Speedwalking is a method of moving from one location in the world to
         another with a minimum of typing.
      For more information on speedwalk modifier characters, see the help for 
         ';addmodifierchar'. For information on speedwalking in general, see the
         help for ';speedwalk'.
         
      This command lists speedwalk modifier characters in the current 
         dictionary.
      
   User commands:
      lmc / listmod / listmodchar / listmodifierchar
